Package com.skobbler.ngx

Contains classes needed for initializing the SKMaps framework.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SKMapsDownloadListener Listener for download operations.
SKPrepareMapTextureListener Listener for events related to preparing map resources needed in order to inialize the library.
 

Class Summary
SKCategories Keeps all suported main categories and categories.
SKCoordinate Stores information about a coordinate.
SKMaps SKMaps provides support for general settings and management that concerns the whole SKMaps SDK.
SKMapsInitSettings Class that stores settings information for initializing the library.
SKPrepareMapTextureThread Handles preparing of map data textures.
SKProxySettings Class used for the proxy used by the framework for internet requests.
SKStorageManager Handles multiple storage methods.
 

Enum Summary
SKCategories.SKPOICategory Specifies types of categories for an SKSearchResult.
SKCategories.SKPOIMainCategory Specifies the main categories.
SKMaps.SKDistanceUnitType Distance unit type enum.
 

Exception Summary
SKDeveloperKeyException Thrown to indicate that the application needs a developer key in order to use it.
SKMapsInitializationException Thrown to indicate that the application has attempted to use the SKMaps library without initializing it.
SKMapsPathsNotInitializedException Thrown to indicate that the application has attempted to initialize SKMaps library, calling SKMaps.initializeSKMaps(android.content.Context, SKMapsInitSettings, String) without setting the paths before.
 

Package com.skobbler.ngx Description

Contains classes needed for initializing the SKMaps framework.
